. Wood et al
</emphasis>
. 26528 (
<collectingRegion box="[551,682,341,367]" country="Bolivia" name="Santa Cruz" pageId="20" pageNumber="221">Santa Cruz</collectingRegion>
, Chiquitos, Desvio Yacuces 
<quantity box="[1012,1062,341,367]" metricMagnitude="3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.0" pageId="20" pageNumber="221" unit="km" value="3.0">3km</quantity>
hacia Valle Hermoso, 
